h2 Install DC/OS on Azure

p.install-time Estimated time: 15min (typical 5 nodes)

p.install-requirements Requires an active cloud subscription with Azure.

p.install-description We currently offer two options to install DC/OS on Azure: an ARM-template based option via the Microsoft Marketplace and a fully managed option via the Azure Container Service.

